name: Cases by Risk Class where Issued Invoice was neither followed by payment or cancelation
query:
SELECT "Risk Class", 
	   COUNT(1) AS "Case Count"
FROM "defaultview-9"
WHERE event_name 
MATCHES ('Create Invoice')
AND
NOT event_name 
MATCHES ('Create Invoice'
		~> 'Receive Payment')
AND
NOT event_name 
MATCHES ('Create Invoice'
		~> 'Cancel Invoice')
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC
